      "rawText": "3:15Mehdi Yakin - Mosaic [JcBATaxSULE]UploadDeep house with organic instrumentation and a steady 122 BPM tempo in the key of G minor, A muted, syncopated electric guitar riff with a clean, slightly compressed tone repeats throughout the track, The percussion features a consistent four-on-the-floor kick drum, crisp off-beat hi-hats, and a sharp clap on beats two and four, A melodic, plucked synth line with a short decay provides a counter-rhythm to the guitar, A warm, sub-heavy bassline follows the kick drum pattern with occasional melodic fills, Atmospheric, filtered synth pads swell in the background, creating harmonic depth, Shaker patterns and subtle woodblock hits add rhythmic complexity to the percussion layer, The arrangement builds through the addition and subtraction of these layers, utilizing low-pass filter sweeps on the pads and melodic elements to manage energy transitions3PublishRemix",
